<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342006>
    bibo:endPage "277" ;
    bibo:issue "2" ;
    bibo:journal "Raffles Bulletin of Zoology" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2009-08-31" ;
    bibo:startPage "255" ;
    bibo:volume "57" ;
    dc:creator "Plant, Adrian R." ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Diversity Of Chelipoda Macquart, 1823 (Diptera: Empididae: Hemerodromiinae) In Northern Thailand With Discussion Of A Biodiversity ‘ Hot Spot’ At Doi Inthanon" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342020>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342018>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342010>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342008> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342020>
    dc:description "Figs. 25–28. Chelipoda species: 25. C. manggawna new species, male; 26. C. macrosceles new species, female habitus; 27. C. nakropa new species, male, front femora showing chaetotaxy; 28. C. hubeiensis Yang & Yang, female, wing. Abbreviations: bm, cell bm; br, cell br; bs, basal spines; d, denticles; dm, cell dm; dm-cu, crossvein dm-cu; s, spines." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5342020/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342018>
    dc:description "Figs. 19–24. Thoracic dorsum of Chelipoda spp. showing schematic pattern of ground colour. 19–20. C. macrosceles new species: 19. male; 20. female: 21. C. flavida Brunneti, male: 22–23. C. nakropa new species, male: 22. high elevation morph; 23. mid elevation morph: 24. C. chaiamnata new species, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5342018/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342010>
    dc:description "Figs. 7–11. Male genitalia of Chelipoda species in lateral view: 7. C. kameawuta new species; 8. C. laisoma new species; 9. C. macrosceles new species; 10. C. manggawna new species; 11. C. meenamluang new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5342010/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342008>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–6. Male genitalia of Chelipoda species in lateral view: 1. C. chaiamnata new species; 2. C. flavida Brunetti; 3. C. guangxiensis Yang & Yang; 4. C. inthawichayanona new species: 5–6 C. hubeiensis Yang & Yang; 5. typical form; 6. variant (outline only)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5342008/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

